OL,4,Cpandemic of knife crime in our country'
OL,6,FHe pointed towards what he calls a
OL,7,Fpandemic of knife crime and said he
OL,8,Fand director Philip Barantini, came up
OL,9,Fwith the idea for the drama after
OL,10,Fhearing news stories of teenage
OL,11,Fstabbings, particularly of young boys
OL,12,Fattacking girls.
OL,14,FGraham admitted that when he sees the
OL,15,Fnews, he can be quick to judge, like
OL,16,Fmany, and blame the parents. He wanted
OL,17,Fto highlight how that is not always
OL,18,Fthe case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
