OL,6,F"There was no social media in our
OL,7,Fday," added Barantini. "But there's so
OL,8,Fmuch out there now and it's so
OL,9,Faccessible.
OL,11,F"There are things that send kids down
OL,12,Fa rabbit hole and they believe that to
OL,13,Fbe true. It's a scary time. I've got
OL,14,Fan eight-year-old daughter and I'm
OL,15,Fscared for the future."
OL,17,FHis advice to parents is simple: "Talk
OL,18,Fto your kids."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
